quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  20,88,"Nuko (muri ya mitako yajugunywe mu muriro, Samiriyu) ababumbiramo akamasa kameze nk’akabira, maze (bamwe muri bo) baravuga bati \"Iyi ni yo mana yanyu,ikaba ari na yo mana ya Musa, uretse ko (Musa)yibagiwe (imana ye)"
  20,89,"Ese ntibabona ko (iyo mana) itagira ijambo (na rimwe) yabasubiza, ndetse ko nta n’ubushobozi ifite bwo kugira ikibi yabatwara cyangwa ngo igire icyiza yabamarira"
  20,90,"Kandi rwose Haruna yari yarabibabwiye na mbere, ati \"Yemwe bantu banjye! Mu by’ukuri, mwaguye mu kigeragezo (cyo gusenga akamasa), kandi mu by’ukuri, Nyagasani wanyu ni (Allah) Nyirimpuhwe; bityo nimunkurikire kandi mwumvire itegeko ryanjye"
  20,91,"Baravuga bati \"Ntituzigera tureka kuyisenga (ako kamasa) kugeza igihe Musa azagarukira"
  20,92,"(Ubwo Musa yari agarutse) yaravuze ati \"YeweHaruna! Ubwo wabonaga bamaze kuyoba, ni iki cyakubujije"
  20,93,Kunkurikira (kugira ngo uze ubimbwire)? Ese wigometse ku itegeko ryanjye
  20,94,"(Haruna) aravuga ati \"Mwana wa mama! Winkurura ubwanwa unanjegeza umutwe! Mu by’ukuri, natinye ko uzavuga ko natandukanyije bene Isiraheli, nkaba ntaranubahirije ijambo ryawe"
  20,95,"(Musa) aravuga ati \"Wabitewe ni iki, yewe Samiriyu"
  20,96,"(Samiriyu) aravuga ati \"Nabonye ibyo batabashije kubona, nuko mfata mu kiganza igitaka cy’aho (ifarasi ya Malayika Gaburiyeli) yakandagiye nkinaga (mu muriro). Uko ni ko nibwiye"
  20,97,"Musa aravuga ati \"Hoshi genda! Kandi (igihano cyawe) mu buzima, kizaba kubaho uvuga uti \"Ntunkoreho (uzabaho uri igicibwa)! Kandi ufite n’isezerano (ryo guhanwa) utazagira aho uhungira. Ikindi kandi reba iki kigirwamana cyawe wahoraga usenga, turagitwika ntakabuza, maze dute ivu ryacyo mu nyanja"
  20,98,Rwose (mwa bantu mwe) Imana yanyu ni Allah wenyine. Nta yindi mana ikwiye gusengwa by’ukuri uretse we. Azi buri kintu cyose